snippet.title: Mega Flappy Sis - SEGA Mega Drive Homebrew Gameplay
snippet.description:
Developed by Lennart Borg (formerly Brink-Abeler), this Flappy Bird clone for the Mega Drive was the first game ever developed by Beetroot Games.

Download: https://harlequin.itch.io/mega-flappy-sys
